org.gearvrf

Interface IAssetEvents

  • All Superinterfaces:
    IEvents
    All Known Implementing Classes:
    GVRAssetLoader.AssetRequest

    public interface IAssetEvents
extends IEvents
    Interface for processing asset load events. The asset loader raises an event whenever a texture or a model is loaded. It also raises an event when the entire asset (models and textures) is loaded. This interface lets you observe these events.

    • Method Detail

      • onAssetLoaded

        void onAssetLoaded(GVRContext context,
                   GVRSceneObject model,
                   java.lang.String filePath,
                   java.lang.String errors)
        Called when a model is successfully loaded. This event will not be raised until the model and all of its textures are loaded.
        Parameters:
        context - GVRContext used to load the model
        model - GVRSceneObject root of the model scene graph, null if model did not load.
        filePath - File path or URL of the model.
        errors - String with loading errors or null if successful.

      • onModelLoaded

        void onModelLoaded(GVRContext context,
                   GVRSceneObject model,
                   java.lang.String filePath)
        Called when a model is successfully loaded. This event is raised when the model file is loaded. Texture files may still be loading in the background.
        Parameters:
        context - GVRContext used to load the model
        model - root of the scene graph representing the model.
        filePath - File path or URL of the model.

      • onTextureLoaded

        void onTextureLoaded(GVRContext context,
                     GVRTexture texture,
                     java.lang.String filePath)
        Called when a texture is successfully loaded.
        Parameters:
        context - GVRContext used to load the model
        texture - GVRTexture created from loading the texture file.
        filePath - File path or URL of the texture file.

      • onModelError

        void onModelError(GVRContext context,
                  java.lang.String error,
                  java.lang.String filePath)
        Called when a model cannot be loaded.
        Parameters:
        context - GVRContext used to load the model
        error - error message
        filePath - File path or URL of the model that failed to load.

      • onTextureError

        void onTextureError(GVRContext context,
                    java.lang.String error,
                    java.lang.String filePath)
        Called when a texture cannot be loaded.
        Parameters:
        context - GVRContext used to load the model
        error - error message
        filePath - File path or URL of the texture that failed to load.
